1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=The One Who Saved You Was Me=

4
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,590
Please, don't kill me.

5
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:49,960
Zhaoli, please don't kill me.

6
00:00:58,390 --> 00:00:59,230
Grandmother.

7
00:01:01,390 --> 00:01:02,640
Ying Du killed Grandmother.

8
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,870
You killed Grandmother.

9
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,820
(Zhaoli has fallen under an illusion.)

10
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:13,680
Zhaoli,

11
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,120
I am Ying Du.

12
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,430
(So, in your obsession,)

13
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,000
(you truly wish to kill me.)

14
00:01:24,430 --> 00:01:25,920
You killed my grandmother.

15
00:01:26,350 --> 00:01:28,350
It is only right
that you pay with your life.

16
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,640
Your grandmother
guards you most in this world.

17
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:37,200
How could I ever harm her?

18
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:40,840
Your grandmother
guards you most in this world.

19
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,870
How could I ever harm her?

20
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:47,970
♪I wish I could hold you once more♪

21
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:49,480
But I saw it with my own eyes.

22
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:51,070
Whether before or just now,

23
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,920
it was you who killed Grandmother.

24
00:01:53,230 --> 00:01:55,280
(She actually remembers
what happened before.)

25
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:57,430
So, I truly brought you back.

26
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:58,870
Brought me back?

27
00:01:59,790 --> 00:02:00,630
Zhaoli.

28
00:02:00,630 --> 00:02:02,690
♪No way out♪

29
00:02:02,710 --> 00:02:04,870
I used the Bracelet to turn back time,

30
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,230
changing the fate
that claimed your life,

31
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,470
and led you back to now.

32
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:13,870
(Could it be I wronged Ying Du?)

33
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,080
(Yet...)

34
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,590
Ying Du.

35
00:02:19,635 --> 00:02:20,949
Ying Du, what's happening to you?

36
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,800
Ying Du.

37
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:25,830
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

38
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,890
Zhaoli, don't cry.

39
00:02:27,883 --> 00:02:29,030
Perhaps this is for the best.

40
00:02:31,470 --> 00:02:33,470
This way, I won't have to see

41
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,430
you die before my eyes.

42
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:38,340
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

43
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,710
But I've lost the chance

44
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:41,310
to keep you safe anymore.

45
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:43,310
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

46
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,150
Ying Du.

47
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,000
Why has it come to this?

48
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,630
Tell me.

49
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,150
What exactly happened?

50
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,910
You must live.

51
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,520
Ying Du.

52
00:02:53,810 --> 00:02:54,680
Ying Du.

53
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,550
You must live.

54
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,520
Ying Du.

55
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,240
Come here.

56
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,080
Ying Du.

57
00:03:32,782 --> 00:03:34,389
(Everlasting Joy)
You've hurt the ruler.

58
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,360
Yet now, you pretend to care here.

59
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,430
Who are you trying to fool?

60
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,250
Luo Cheng,

61
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,870
you're Ying Du's only trusted aide.

62
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:44,430
You know everything about him.

63
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,400
Tell me.

64
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:47,080
Wasn't he supposed to heal himself?

65
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,560
What happened?

66
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:50,680
What on earth is going on?

67
00:03:52,033 --> 00:03:53,430
You still have the nerve to ask me?

68
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,630
What makes you so worthy

69
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,960
of the ruler's efforts for you?

70
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,080
For me?

71
00:03:58,710 --> 00:03:59,550
Seven days ago,

72
00:04:00,253 --> 00:04:01,910
he suddenly coughed up blood
and fainted.

73
00:04:02,193 --> 00:04:04,150
(Everlasting Joy)
His self-healing was gone then.

74
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:05,800
Even the Bracelet was damaged.

75
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:07,870
Whenever he uses his power,

76
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:10,150
the Frostbite Curse worsens.

77
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:11,840
Yet he ignored his health

78
00:04:11,870 --> 00:04:13,870
and forced his power
to mend the Bracelet.

79
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,120
He said it was to protect you.

80
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:18,070
(Could what Ying Du said be true?)

81
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,630
(He cannot heal himself)

82
00:04:19,701 --> 00:04:21,100
(because he brought me back to life)

83
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,390
(by forcing the Bracelet
to turn back time.)

84
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:25,120
(But I saw him)

85
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,000
(kill Grandmother.)

86
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,720
Why did he kill my people?

87
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:32,310
Those two?

88
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,560
They tormented you

89
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,750
with Wu Luoluo.

90
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,120
His body was at its limits,

91
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,149
yet you still wounded him.

92
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,070
Do you know

93
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,830
that with his current state,

94
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,000
he may lose his life at any moment

95
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,240
and may never wake up again?

96
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,080
Luo Cheng,

97
00:04:51,510 --> 00:04:53,070
there must be a way to save him,

98
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,960
right?

99
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,750
There is no way,

100
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,680
unless we find the legendary Saintess.

101
00:05:01,910 --> 00:05:02,850
(The Saintess?)

102
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,270
Now, your power has awakened,

103
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:07,310
and you've become the Saintess.

104
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:16,360
The ruler's power is unique.

105
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,870
If the Saintess could serve
as the remedy's guide,

106
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:20,470
perhaps

107
00:05:20,613 --> 00:05:23,059
it could temporarily suppress
the Frostbite Curse within him.

108
00:05:27,370 --> 00:05:31,550
♪I wish I could hold you once more♪

109
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:38,600
♪Plant a field of love upon your heart♪

110
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:45,870
♪Twists and turns,
fate leaves no way out♪

111
00:05:47,170 --> 00:05:50,990
♪Chasing through three lifetimes♪

112
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:57,100
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

113
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,840
Zhaoli,

114
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,160
what are you doing?

115
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:06,750
I'm going to save you.

116
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,160
I want you to live well.

117
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:16,880
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

118
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,870
Zhaoli,

119
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,480
dreaming like this,

120
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:25,510
how should I face you when I wake up?

121
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:28,120
Then let's just treat it as a dream.

122
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:30,480
♪And that is enough♪

123
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:34,390
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

124
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:37,340
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

125
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:42,250
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

126
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:49,830
It seems Wu Zhaoli really saved Ying Du.

127
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:54,600
Yan Che's body is reaching its limit.

128
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:57,040
My identity won't stay hidden
for much longer.

129
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:00,680
While Ying Du hasn't recovered,

130
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:03,360
I must act tonight.

131
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,630
Mr. Yan,

132
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,750
your hand...

133
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,960
My hand?

134
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,270
What's wrong?

135
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:25,150
(Ying Du,)

136
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,630
(we share the same bloodline,)

137
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:30,480
(yet you were born with everything,)

138
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,413
(while I'm deemed unworthy
of even a name.)

139
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,950
(You owe me,)

140
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:38,120
(and I'll reclaim it, piece by piece.)

141
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,440
Ying Du,

142
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,510
today marks your final hour.

143
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,160
(It's the man in black.)

144
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,320
Ying Du,

145
00:07:58,750 --> 00:07:59,590
watch out!

146
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,000
It's

147
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,720
Yan Che.

148
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:18,470
Zhaoli,

149
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:19,800
are you hurt?

150
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:23,000
I'm fine.

151
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:26,270
Zhaoli.

152
00:08:27,860 --> 00:08:30,180
(Yan Manor)

153
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:40,200
Unexpectedly, Wu Zhaoli's Saintess Power

154
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,670
has awakened.

155
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,390
My wounds have worsened.

156
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,750
If Wu Zhaoli does not offer

157
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,720
her heart's blood,

158
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,270
I might not have survived.

159
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:02,850
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

160
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:09,650
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

161
00:09:11,110 --> 00:09:14,390
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

162
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:17,290
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

163
00:09:17,810 --> 00:09:23,100
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

164
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:26,800
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

165
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:29,500
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

166
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:33,540
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

167
